{"tid":106603,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(內有丁圖)求救...有冇好獸醫介紹","createTime":"2017-02-03T18:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T09:33:12.000Z","uid":80734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7729970ba7ad81b726dc047875fa198b8dd35c","tid":106603,"uid":80734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:34:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的，屋企隻貓b入左屋一個月左右不時打下乞嚏，帶佢去睇獸醫嘅時候獸醫話冇咩咁就冇理。<br />\n<br />\n點知之後就到另一隻半歲大嘅隻左眼不時紅腫同流眼水、瘋狂眨眼，但又冇角膜潰瘍（醫生檢查過）。醫生檢查完都講唔出咩事，淨係開左啲眼膏就算，但揸完兩日又賴返嘢......最近啱啱好返啲冇再復發。<br />\n<br />\n結果啱啱返到屋企見到入屋一個月嘅貓b隻眼都腫埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢兩隻都食得瞓得又玩得，睇過3個醫生都完全唔知咩事，好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇貓奴有好醫生介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/04/023115_fadba86f29f4f92e9225cef2b453e965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F023115_fadba86f29f4f92e9225cef2b453e965.jpg&h=0cf6eaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n半歲大嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/04/023419_28a8351077c62bdd1c01375630c9a2ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F023419_28a8351077c62bdd1c01375630c9a2ff.jpg&h=9bca5d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出事嗰兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6b1f761511b7f405b82c8365fb983ffc5a7357","tid":106603,"uid":6902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:41:49.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e2aa66dba5340ac2e03215a9bb3814a055c288d8","tid":106603,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"平既太子npv<br />\n好啲既荃灣享和"},{"pid":"ec8bd077a07d3cebf1eeed9f47c1203ffd513757","tid":106603,"uid":81282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T19:02:20.000Z","msg":"幫推，希望貓貓快啲好返"},{"pid":"123e908a8bff7720a70a903d9b591c8d566220fd","tid":106603,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T19:35:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"180da81b3c7d4f606e3add7dcf78c8a1c4bf0e13","tid":106603,"uid":44066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T19:45:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會係啲貓一齊玩（打交）果陣搲到？"},{"pid":"9ef177fa7a6685a84b83840a0708eab775d54038","tid":106603,"uid":16642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T19:48:48.000Z","msg":"眼屎分泌係咩色？"},{"pid":"db0b374807889f8cd1c6067b35979ff75f97bf14","tid":106603,"uid":80734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T20:18:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係啲貓一齊玩（打交）果陣搲到？</blockquote><br />\n開頭都係咁諗，但之後分開過佢地都照出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bf3a5e370448f0d8aed1dc52bc20c67d3c8d74","tid":106603,"uid":80734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T20:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼屎分泌係咩色？</blockquote><br />\n白色偏黃，半歲嗰隻試過有次粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa584c48aa4fc0498f28947c4a461206f96ca49","tid":106603,"uid":80734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T20:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平既太子npv<br />\n好啲既荃灣享和</blockquote><br />\n有冇話要指定咩醫生咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322477789a97d69af02735a196d63c3d77c67015","tid":106603,"uid":47681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T20:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平既太子npv<br />\n好啲既荃灣享和</blockquote><br />\n有冇話要指定咩醫生咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n享和我睇開陳醫生，但如果唔接新症/放假<br />\n可以睇梁醫生/張醫生（3個都係男人）"},{"pid":"81235c1497ed45534d95987bdd68f1f7eb23496f","tid":106603,"uid":16642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T20:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>眼屎分泌係咩色？</blockquote><br />\n白色偏黃，半歲嗰隻試過有次粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前貓仔兩個月大成日跑 唔知係咪撞親都試過咁<br />\n紅左一星期 分泌物黃黃綠綠<br />\n滴左幾日消炎眼水就無事<br />\n唔使太擔心既 反而觀察下佢地有無打交同屋企有無易撞到眼既地方（以貓仔身高）"},{"pid":"d5b1759ffb0c43cc16d0ebecd10ace8eec4cc3f4","tid":106603,"uid":81915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:20:07.000Z","msg":"嘉名動物診所<br />\n<br />\n屋企主人由細睇到大，診所得一個醫生無姑娘，董醫生都幾細心，價錢好合理。係深水埗可以參考一下。"},{"pid":"b7a3e93be064e7876e2c53d04574711b75f797d6","tid":106603,"uid":63337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"cat flu <br />\n好多貓仔都有過<br />\n我兩隻貓初黎報到都有過"},{"pid":"392a2ea79ee442d0802a2d09f3d41622866efe09","tid":106603,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平既太子npv<br />\n好啲既荃灣享和</blockquote><br />\n有冇話要指定咩醫生咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n享和我睇開陳醫生，但如果唔接新症/放假<br />\n可以睇梁醫生/張醫生（3個都係男人）</blockquote><br />\nyes台灣人陳醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d5a1d58fb20b2c86df4bdf8dacf173c06219c8","tid":106603,"uid":80734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>眼屎分泌係咩色？</blockquote><br />\n白色偏黃，半歲嗰隻試過有次粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前貓仔兩個月大成日跑 唔知係咪撞親都試過咁<br />\n紅左一星期 分泌物黃黃綠綠<br />\n滴左幾日消炎眼水就無事<br />\n唔使太擔心既 反而觀察下佢地有無打交同屋企有無易撞到眼既地方（以貓仔身高）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭以為打交搞成咁，但分開左都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次搽完藥膏仲要嚴重左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828f2acacebd538b903302fea9b61b72ad0359b5","tid":106603,"uid":80734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cat flu <br />\n好多貓仔都有過<br />\n我兩隻貓初黎報到都有過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我隻大貓以前黎嗰陣都有<br />\n但同佢地好似有啲唔同<br />\n佢地係勁反反覆覆 隔一日就腫一次咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}